::DarkMouse::

"DarkMouse, TERRORIZE"  transformes into mouse mode.
"COMPUTER, AUTOGUNS SET TO READY ON INTRUDER!"
The computer autoguns system rotated all the internal guns and 
focused on Lockjaw.

"ONE MORE MOVE AND YOUR HISTORY PAL."
She wasn't about to let a bot with more bolts than brains just waltz 
into the base and try to hurt one of her commanders.  Her programming 
wouldn't allow it.
